rea. He is currently 26 years old. He is the younger brother of singer Joo. While he may be a talented personality, recently, he has been facing a legal problem.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Jung Il-hoon Sentenced 2 Years In Prison For The Use Of Marijuana</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The singer Jung Il-hoon was&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thestar.com.my/lifestyle/entertainment/2021/06/10/jung-ilhoon-of-k-pop-group-btob-sentenced-to-2-years-in-prison-fined-rm491k-for-buying-and-using-marijuana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sentenced to two years</a>&nbsp;in prison and fined 133 million won ($119,639) on 10 June 2021 for purchasing and using marijuana on 161 occasions, through three years starting from July 2016 up till January 2019.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ezoic-pub-video-placeholder-1\" class=\"ezoic-videopicker-video\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon was immediately taken into custody after the ruling was announced. He also had a group of seven accomplices with him, who were all sentenced to prison terms ranging from 1.5 to 2 years.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Earlier, in the court hearing prior to this, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://meaww.com/btob-eunkwang-public-apology-fans-questionable-controversial-gesture-ilhoon-departure-band-reactions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">prosecutions demanded</a>&nbsp;a four-year prison sentence for Jung, along with the 133 million forfeiture. However, after this, Jung admitted to the charges and made a mercy plea, which led to a shorter sentence. The rapper had also left the boy band BtoB back in December 2020, after the news of his drug use came out.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Last December, Korean channel Channel A reported that the police investigated Ilhoon for marijuana use, and the drug was detected in his hair. It said that to avoid detection, Ilhoon<a href=\"https://www.straitstimes.com/life/entertainment/former-btob-member-ilhoon-admits-to-buying-and-using-marijuana-at-first-court\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">&nbsp;used cryptocurrency to buy</a>&nbsp;marijuana. He deposited cash in an account of an acquaintance who converted it to cryptocurrency to buy marijuana.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon had&nbsp;<a href=\"https://voi.id/en/lifestyle/24828/tertangkap-konsumsi-mariyuana-ilhoon-pilih-keluar-dari-btob\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">postponed his mandatory military service</a>, which was supposed to be carried out in March due to the COVID-19 pandemic. However, the rapper recently served in the military during the year 2020.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">When Ilhoon’s drug use allegations came to light, he was called up for trial in court on 22 April. According to the prosecution, Jung Ilhoon conspired with the other defendants from 6 July 2016 to 9 January 2019, spending over 130 million won ($116,400) for drugs and smoking a total of 826g marijuana 161 times.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/298602/20210422/former-btob-ilhoon-admits-smoking-marijuana-161-times-first-trial.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">admitted to his charges</a>,<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“I’m sincerely reflecting on my mistakes. I’m really sorry,”</span>&nbsp;the rapper said. The legal counsel noted,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“The defendant is reflecting deeply on his actions. He was fearful as it was the first trial and investigation of his life. He worked in the entertainment industry at such a young age and he tried to relieve the stress in the wrong way.”</span></span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Net Worth And Career Of Jung Il-hoon</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">With his endeavor throughout the years in the music industry, Jung Il-hoon has earned lots of fame and wealth in his name. Though his net worth is still in review, he may have accumulated millions of dollars to his name through his works in his professional career.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">During G.NA’s debut promotion in 2010, Jung filled in some of Yong Junhyung’s parts during G.NA’s performance on a music show for the song<em>&nbsp;I’ll Back Off So You Can Live Better</em>. His debut as an actor was in 2011 through the JTBC sitcom&nbsp;<em>I Live</em>&nbsp;in Cheongdam Dong.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Jung debuted as the main rapper of the boy band BtoB in 2012 with the group’s official debut on Mnet’s&nbsp;<em>M! Countdown</em>&nbsp;on 21 March 2021. The band BtoB became quite prominent in the Korean music industry,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.allkpop.com/article/2021/04/the-highest-earning-groups-based-on-their-appearance-fees-in-south-korea\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">earning them over</a>&nbsp;$45,000 per appearance in an event. Ilhoon also became a special MC along with Bomi from&nbsp;<em>Apink</em>&nbsp;from 2012 until the 206th&nbsp;episode. In 2015, he starred in the web drama, Webtoon Hero: Tundra Show as the lead actor, portraying Kim Sung-min.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px;\"><img class=\" jch-lazyloaded\" src=\"https://glamourbiz.com/images/uploads/jung-il-hoon-with-other-btob-members.jpg\" data-src=\"/images/uploads/jung-il-hoon-with-other-btob-members.jpg\" alt=\"jung il hoon with other btob members\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Jung Il-hoon with other BTOB members (©: allkpop)</span></em></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon as a singer has been featured in several songs, including G.NA’s&nbsp;<em>Oops!</em>, 2YOON’s<em>&nbsp;Nightmare</em>, HyunA’s&nbsp;<em>Roll Deep</em>, Samuel’s&nbsp;<em>ONE</em>, Yoo Sung Eun’s&nbsp;<em>Hug me</em>, as well as FT.Island’s Lee Hongki’s solo song&nbsp;<em>COOKIES</em>. He also joined Unpretty Rapster 3, the beauty shows The Cushion, and co-hosted Weekly Idol from 2012-1016. As a solo artist, he released his solo debut with&nbsp;<em>She’s Gone MV</em>&nbsp;and his solo debut album titled&nbsp;<em>Big Wave</em>&nbsp;in 2018. He has also collaborated in several songs, including&nbsp;<em>My Love By My Side</em>&nbsp;with Heo Ga-Yoon and&nbsp;<em>Baesisi</em>&nbsp;with Jisook.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">On 31 December 2020, Cube Entertainment announced his departure from BtoB after being investigated by the police for marijuana usage. Ilhoon left the band because he felt responsible for breaking the trust of his fans, and still, the fans were devastated to see a band member left, and they reacted to the news on the internet with several posts.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/kfanaticsforevs/status/1344558614283862021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">One fan</a>&nbsp;wrote:&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“BTOB will never be the same without Jung Ilhoon.”</span>&nbsp;While&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BTOBfnccnt/status/1344521314351030274\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">another one</a>&nbsp;said:&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“BTOB songs will be different without Ilhoon’s voice in it.”</span>&nbsp;Many members of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ilhoonsubi/status/1344541176322408453\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BTOB fandom have pledged</a>&nbsp;to continue supporting him.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“I will never let go of your hands and I will continue to support you no matter what happens. You will always and forever be our BTOB’S JUNG ILHOON”,</span>&nbsp;said one fan. Another Twitter user said:<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“I respect you Ilhoon… Respect your decision. You were thinking about your BTOB brother in making this decision right?”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">With this much love and support from his fans, it may not be a surprise if he decided to return to the band after serving his time in prison, reflecting on his action.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Does Jung Il-hoon Have A Girlfriend?</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">While Jung Il-hoon may be a prominent personality in the industry, he has not had any dating or relationship history to date. However, it’s not that he doesn’t want to date anyone.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon once revealed his taste or ideal type of woman he wants, saying that she should have<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“long eyelashes, big eyes, s line figure, slender body, it doesn’t matter if she is tall or short, has white skin, has brown colored pupils, it would be good if she has short bob hair.”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Considering the statements, many girls may be thinking of giving a strong impression if she ever met Ilhoon. Moreover,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://kfanatics.com/pros-cons-dating-btob-member/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">kfanatics.com</a>&nbsp;has even released some pros and cons for the girls out there who are considering date Ilhoon. The pros listed as, he would show&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“you the original version of Gwiyomi,”</span>&nbsp;give out lots of gifts from Gucci, and he has a perfect sense of things, has an outstanding ethic, and cares about image. Meanwhile, the con in dating him is that<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“You might not understand some words when you quarrel as he talks fast being a rapper himself.”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ilhoon is also quite the fun guy. He once went to BTOB’s official Twitter account&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dkpopnews.net/2013/08/btobs-ilhoon-reveals-hyunsiks-girlfriend.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">to reveal fellow member Hyunsik’s girlfriend</a>. In August of 2013, he first tweeted,<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“Heol BTOB Hyunsik’s girlfriend”</span>&nbsp;and followed up,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“that’s me,”</span>&nbsp;attaching a photo of his cross-dressing and wearing a wig.</span></p>', '2021-06-27 10:52:32.030449', '2021-07-01 03:09:47.745621', '2021-07-01 03:09:47.745621', 1, 1, 1, 1, '2021-06-29 14:40:07.184573', 'BTOB Ex-Member Jung Il-hoon Sentenced 2 Years In Prison For The Use Of Marijuana | Net Worth & Girlfriend', 'BTOB Ex-Member Jung Il-hoon Sentenced 2 Years In Prison For The Use Of Marijuana | Net Worth & Girlfriend', 21, 1, 1, 8, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 8);
INSERT INTO `blogs_blog` (`id`, `title`, `alias`, `introtext`, `displayphoto`, `research_data`, `fulltext`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `checked_out_time`, `published`, `researched`, `authored`, `edited`, `published_date`, `metakey`, `metadesc`, `hits`, `featured`, `authored_by`, `cat_id_id`, `checked_out_by`, `created_by`, `edited_by`, `modified_by`, `published_by`, `researched_by`, `tags`, `version`) VALUES
(3, 'Who Is Blair Underwood Wife Desiree DaCosta? Their 27 Years Marriage Comes To An End', 'who-is-blair-underwood-wife-desiree-dacosta-their-27-years-marriage-comes-to-an-end', 'Who Is Blair Underwood Wife Desiree DaCosta? Their 27 Years Marriage Comes To An End', '\\images\\blogimages\\XS8NHL1625106739.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Desiree DaCosta is well recognized for being the wife of actor Blair Underwood. She is also named as the American Executive Assistant for Eddie Murphy.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">She is famous for her work in the romance and drama film&nbsp;<em>Boomerang, released</em>&nbsp;on 1 July 1992. Desiree later left the entertainment industry after her marriage to Blair. And after being together for 27 years in marriage, their relationship seems to have reached an end.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Desiree DaCosta Seeks Divorce From Husband Blair Underwood After 27 Years In Marriage</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The decades-long pair Desiree DaCosta and her husband, Blair Underwood, have announced they are going separate ways after 27 years of marriage.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ezoic-pub-video-placeholder-1\" class=\"ezoic-videopicker-video\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The couple, who shares three children, announced their split in a joint social media statement. They shared it on Instagram on 31 May 2021 to announce their split.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“After a tremendous amount of thought prayer and work on ourselves individually and collectively, we have come to the conclusion to end our marriage thatbegan 27 years ago,”</span>&nbsp;the statement began.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“It has truly been a beautiful journey,”</span>&nbsp;they continued in their joint statement.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The statement further read that their<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“proudest achievements are our three incredible children”</span>&nbsp;who were entrusted to them by “God,” for them, they will find their best interest and will “continue to do so.”</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Furthermore, the duo noted their plans to split amicably – hoping to remain “the best of friends” and be good co-parents to their children despite them going different ways.<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“We thank you for all your support throughout the years and we humbly ask for privacy and understanding during this new season of change,”</span>&nbsp;the message concluded.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji