(4, 'Charlie Hanson Got Removed From Netflix Series \'After Life\' After Sexual Allegations | Age, & Bio', 'charlie-hanson-got-removed-from-netflix-series-after-life-after-sexual-allegations-age-bio', 'Charlie Hanson Got Removed From Netflix Series \'After Life\' After Sexual Allegations | Age, & Bio', '\\images\\blogimages\\O0B60Q1625106758.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Charlie Hanson is a notable personality in the field of directing and producing films and TV shows. He is mostly known for his work on Netflix’s After Life. His award-winning work includes television shows such as Desmond’s, Chef!, The Big Impression, The Sketch Show and Whites, and the 2003 feature film A Way of Life.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Hanson has stayed mostly prominent for his work in the entertainment field. But, in 2021, certain news surfaced which may further lead to his downfall in his career.</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Charlie Hanson Got Removed From Netflix Series \'After Life\' After Sexual Allegations</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Netflix has confirmed that producer Charlie Hanson has been removed from After Life in response to the allegations and at the request of his accusers.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ezoic-pub-video-placeholder-1\" class=\"ezoic-videopicker-video\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Hanson also had his BAFTA membership suspended after women reported incidents of historical sexual misconduct this week.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Several sources said the producer is alleged to have preyed on 11 different women. The accusers claimed that he preyed on the women when they were young, “promising them a starry career under his wing” before making unwanted sexual advances.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tv-producer-charlie-hanson-faces-sex-claims-9hf9ck66m\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">allegations lodged</a>&nbsp;against him – including incidents of serious sexual assault – date from 2008 and 2015.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Ricky Gervais, who worked with Hanson on sitcoms&nbsp;<em>Derek and Extras</em>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/charlie-hanson-ricky-gervais-after-life-b1856559.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">responded to the allegations</a>&nbsp;made against him by removing him from the production of his hit Netflix series. He also released a statement, saying,<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“I am shocked and appalled to learn of the historical allegations made by a number of women against Charlie Hanson.”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“The decision was made to immediately remove him from production and I am confident the matter is being handled thoroughly,”</span>&nbsp;he added.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px;\"><img class=\" jch-lazyloaded\" src=\"https://glamourbiz.com/images/uploads/charlie-hanson-and-ricky-gervais.jpg\" data-src=\"/images/uploads/charlie-hanson-and-ricky-gervais.jpg\" alt=\"charlie hanson and ricky gervais\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Charlie Hanson and Ricky Gervais (©: BBC)</span></em></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The women have written to BAFTA and Netflix, outlining the allegations, while Hanson denies those claims and said he would fully co-operate with an investigation.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Among the alleged victims is one woman who says she met Hanson in 2008 to discuss a script and had non-consensual sex with him – an alleged incident that left her “traumatized.” Another claims the showrunner “acted as a mentor,” introducing her to industry contacts before sexually assaulting her at her home in 2015 when she was too to consent.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">In the 5,000 word email,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tv-producer-charlie-hanson-faces-sex-claims-9hf9ck66m\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the woman alleged</a>:&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">“Charlie Hanson is a predator who uses his reputation, connections and standing in order to groom far younger, impressionable and sometimes vulnerable women into trusting him,”</span>&nbsp;the writing continued,<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“At times he will promise them a starry career under his wing, and then exploits that trust in creepy and illegal ways.”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Meanwhile, Hanson says that the accusations made against him are anonymous and “are demonstrably false,” so he would go to length for protecting and restoring his reputation. He further added to fully cooperate for the investigations of the allegations made against him.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9633823/11-women-accuse-Life-producer-Charlie-Hanson-sexual-assault.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">In a statement</a>, BAFTA said:<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;“Bafta is an arts charity and does not have the power to investigate historical claims of abuse therefore we have referred the matter to the police. The behavior that these accounts allege is abhorrent, in complete opposition to Bafta values and has no place in the industry.”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family