ple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">The actress Allison, who pleaded guilty to several charges for her involvement with the controversial, cult-like self-help group NXIVM,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://people.com/crime/allison-mack-files-for-divorce-nicki-clyne/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">filed for divorce</a>&nbsp;from her wife, Nicki Clyne, in December 2020.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Mack filed for divorce from the actress Clyne in Orange County, California, in early December 2020, according to&nbsp;<em>TMZ</em>. They tied the knot back in February 2017.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 13.3333px;\"><img class=\" jch-lazyloaded\" src=\"https://glamourbiz.com/images/uploads/allison-mack-and-partner-nicki-clyne.jpg\" data-src=\"/images/uploads/allison-mack-and-partner-nicki-clyne.jpg\" alt=\"allison mack and partner nicki clyne\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); f